'''塞夫顿山'''（[[英語|英語]]：Mount Sefton，[[毛利语|毛利语]]：Maukatua）是[[新西兰|新西兰]][[南阿爾卑斯山脈|南阿爾卑斯山脈]]阿罗阿罗凯赫山脉（Aroarokaehe Range）的一座山，位於[[庫克山|庫克山]]以南12公里<ref>{{Cite news|publisher={{link-en|The Timaru Herald}}|date=3 Apr 2013|author=Matthew Littlewood|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/timaru-herald/news/8500887/Dual-names-accepted-in-Aoraki-Mt-Cook|title=Dual names accepted in Aoraki-Mt Cook|accessdate=2016-08-25|archive-date=2020-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614133929/http://www.stuff.co.nz/timaru-herald/news/8500887/Dual-names-accepted-in-Aoraki-Mt-Cook|dead-url=no}}</ref>。塞夫顿山高3151米，是南阿尔卑斯山的第13高的山峰。該山在[[毛利語|毛利語]]中的意思是眾神之山。該山於1894年的聖誕節首次有人登頂 <ref name="Rose1929">{{Cite book|last=Rose|first=John Holland|title=The Cambridge History of the British Empire|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=mSY9AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA43|accessdate=23 May 2015|year=1929|publisher=[[劍橋大學出版社|劍橋大學出版社]]|pages=43ff}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Mountaineering - Aoraki/Mt Cook|url=https://teara.govt.nz/en/mountaineering/page-3|accessdate=5 December 2020|author=Wilson|first=John|publisher={{link-en|Te Ara: The Encyclopedia of New Zealand}}|archive-date=2013-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116075743/http://www.teara.govt.nz/en/mountaineering/3|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
